Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.http.api.service.mapping

Annotation Type APIUses

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target({TYPE,FIELD})
@Repeatable(APIUsesRepeatable.class)
public @interface APIUses
    This annotation is used to bind subclasses of HttpAPI with their default settings such as default root of API (at this case the annotation should be used with URLValuePropertySupplier) and a set of request tuners (at this case the annotation should be used with RequestTuner).

    This annotation may mark classes which implement URLValuePropertySupplier or RequestTuner or fields of enums which implement URLValuePropertySupplier.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element Description
      java.lang.Class<? extends HttpAPI> usedBy  

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
